{"type":"message","id":"c83fb657","parentId":"2800cc57","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:30:00.079Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:321d856c-eb47-44d0-a1de-24fd64d31f4f 盘后复盘+邮件报告] 执行每日盘后复盘：\n\n第一步：检查今天是否为交易日\n- 如果是周末或法定节假日，直接输出\"今日休市，跳过盘后任务\"并结束\n- 2026年工作日休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216 20260217 20260218 20260219 20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001 20261002 20261005 20261006 20261007\n\n第二步：SSH 拉取数据\n- 读取 E:\\Quant\\Datas\\positions.json（持仓）\n- 读取 E:\\Quant\\Datas\\daily_result.json（交易结果）\n- 读取 E:\\Quant\\strategies\\logs\\trader_YYYYMMDD.log（执行日志）\n\n第三步：用 Tushare 查今日行情（不要用Baostock）\n- 通过 sys.path.insert + _get_token() 获取 token\n- 查持仓股今日 open/high/low/close/pct_chg\n- 查上证指数今日表现\n\n第四步：生成复盘报告\n- 持仓盈亏分析\n- 大盘对比\n- 因子有效性追踪\n- 存到 strategies/reports/post_market_review_YYYYMMDD.md\n\n第五步：发邮件\n- 收件人 958500892@qq.com，抄送 l1cheeyuan@163.com\n- 用 Gmail SMTP（smtp.gmail.com:587，App Password jsnjyjwpavymplev）\n\n注意：\n- 数据源优先级：Tushare(主力) > Baostock(备选)\n- SSH 密码从 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 的 env.SSH_PASSWORD 读取\nCurrent time: Monday, April 6th, 2026 — 18:30 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-06 10:30 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775471400078}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8d5fed0","parentId":"c83fb657","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:30:32.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nThe user is asking me to execute a daily post-market review with email report. This is a cron task that has specific steps to follow. Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. Check if today is a trading day (2026-04-06)\n2. SSH to pull data from the cloud server\n3. Use Tushare to get today's market data\n4. Generate a post-market review report\n5. Send email\n\nLet me start by checking if today is a trading day. Looking at the list provided:\n2026年工作日休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216 20260217 20260218 20260219 20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001 20261002 20261005 20261006 20261007\n\nToday is 2026-04-06, which is in the list! So this is a holiday and I should output \"今日休市，跳过盘后任务\" and end.\n\nBut wait, let me double-check. The current time shows Monday, April 6th, 2026 — 18:30 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-06 10:30 UTC. And 20260406 is indeed in the holiday list.\n\nSo I should just output that message and end.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<thinking>\n根据用户提供的信息，今天是2026年4月6日。我需要检查休市日列表：\n\n2026年工作日休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216 20260217 20260218 20260219 20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001 20261002 20261005 20261006 20261007\n\n今天2026-04-06正好在休市日列表中，因此是法定节假日，A股休市。\n</thinking>\n\n今日休市，跳过盘后任务"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":33545,"output":492,"cacheRead":8283,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775471400079}}
